➜广西诗人陈熠明：天涯彼岸领航人
http://www.sohu.com/a/431148146_100115135	36470
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201111/42c7b1b5fb524d1c884c9f2950b48766.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天涯彼岸领航人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·知识海燕领潮人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春风彼岸红霞远，智慧渊博浪里深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦想兰舟霜雨过，知识海燕领潮人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·无涯海上指南针</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">知识彼岸问渊深，浩瀚天涯引浪神。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里兰舟风雨路，无涯海上指南针。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(三)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·两鬓春华玉雪霜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">热血丹心风雨路，留香笔墨写辉煌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花开满院红桃李，两鬓春华玉雪霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201111/4047ca1fa37547dc9ff786522674706e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
